  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Obično <span class=\"highlighted-text\">become</span> se povezuje sa promenom u nešto što ranije nije bilo.</p>\n<p>To znači da nisi bio ovisnik od kafe prije pridruživanja kompaniji, ali sada jesi. <span class=\"highlighted-text\">I became addicted to coffee when I started working at the company</span> (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">became</span> ni wakati uliopita wa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">become</span>),</p>\n<p>U vreme <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Present Perfect</span>, koristiš formu <span class=\"highlighted-text\">become</span> nakon <span class=\"highlighted-text\">have</span> ili <span class=\"highlighted-text\">has</span>, što znači da je promena koja ti se nastavlja uticati na život. Na primer, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">I've become interested in video games at age 20</span>.</p>\n</section>",
